    "description": "无忧无虑生活在荒岛之上的你，原本过着打打野猪，偶尔骚扰一下野人族群的悠闲生活，但是自从你救下那名因为空难而流落到这个荒岛的美女之后，你的生活就发生了改变。<br>游戏玩法<br>收集地图上散落的材料和补给，用来制造对抗危险的装备和采集树木矿藏的工具；建设并升级你的住房，制造生存下去的必需品，将您的住房建设成温馨小屋。请随时注意你和你的伴侣的饱食度，口渴度和血量，一旦血量归零游戏将会结束。<br><br>游戏特色：<br>自定义美女头像，根据你上传的照片，我们自动生成对应的3D模型，以满足你的各种幻想。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/9a3e1af769bb57763b2cd66973c91249.avif?t=1659766381\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/3dbc4044381281a22d5ae1a3dbab5a98.poster.avif?t=1659766381\" width=400 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/3dbc4044381281a22d5ae1a3dbab5a98.webm?t=1659766381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/3dbc4044381281a22d5ae1a3dbab5a98.mp4?t=1659766381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>“挖矿”、“砍树”获取基本资源，但是岛上的资源的总量是有限的，合理利用资源，才能获得更好的生活。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/4ec6daa2a5b1feea84e35e0264ce82af.avif?t=1659766381\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/6ae4d55224deb723c835b34a6ad9c7b3.poster.avif?t=1659766381\" width=400 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/6ae4d55224deb723c835b34a6ad9c7b3.webm?t=1659766381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/6ae4d55224deb723c835b34a6ad9c7b3.mp4?t=1659766381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>自由建造，想建什么就建什么。随心打造自己的荒岛住宅。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/997e83d56c837d1bb743dafa44c4c18c.poster.avif?t=1659766381\" width=400 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/997e83d56c837d1bb743dafa44c4c18c.webm?t=1659766381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/997e83d56c837d1bb743dafa44c4c18c.mp4?t=1659766381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>为了保护您的荒岛生活更安全，我们为您准备了从弓箭到标枪甚至于枪械的武器建造系统。以及多种服饰装扮供您自由选择。<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/736733a520be4ea69e852025a038f7d0.poster.avif?t=1659766381\" width=400 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/736733a520be4ea69e852025a038f7d0.webm?t=1659766381\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855610/extras/736733a520be4ea69e852025a038f7d0.mp4?t=1659766381\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏操作方式<br>[W]、[A]、[S]、[D]控制角色行动<br>[E] 与场景进行交互<br>数字1~6快捷键切换使用物品<br>[Shift] 加速<br>[Space] 跳跃<br>[C] 下蹲<br><strong> 背包<br><br>鼠标左键攻击<br>鼠标右键瞄准<br>打开建造蓝图，鼠标滚轮进行选择<br>打开建造蓝图，鼠标左键放置物体<br>打开建造蓝图，鼠标右键选择可建造的物体</strong>",
